reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight compression packing cubes
reviews.reviewText: I tend to overpack so compression packing cubes have been a space saver for me. This set includes 3 compression packing cubes. You get one small, one medium, one large compression cube. The packing cubes are made of a nylon material, so they’re easy to wipe clean after a trip. The material also makes them lightweight. With these packing cubes you have the option of using them as regular packing cubes or as a compression one by utilizing the compression zipper. The zippers on the packing cubes have an extended cord allowing for more control when you open and close them. Overall, this is a good set if you’re looking for a variety of packing cubes sizes.
